<html>
<head>
  <style>
    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-Regular.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 100 400;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-RegularItalic.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 100 400;
      font-style: italic;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-Medium.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 500 600;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-MediumItalic.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 500 600;
      font-style: italic;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-Bold.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 700 800;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-BoldItalic.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 700 800;
      font-style: italic;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-BlackItalic.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 900;
      font-style: italic;
      font-display: swap;
    }

    @font-face {
      font-family: "CircularStd";
      src: url("https://s3-sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/execution-mode.s3.getbud.co/auth0/fonts/CircularStd-Black.woff2") format("woff2");
      font-weight: 900;
      font-style: normal;
      font-display: swap;
    }
  </style>

</head>

<body style="background-color: #EEF2FC; padding: 34px 0;">
<center>
  <div
    style='
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 44px 24px;
            border-collapse: collapse !important;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            width: 560px;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 56px rgba(83, 83, 191, 0.07);
            font-family: "CircularStd", Arial, sans-serif;
          '
  >
    <img
      src="https://s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/html-bag.s3.getbud.co/branding/bud-logotype-sm.png"
      alt="Logotipo do Bud"
      width="105px"
      height="auto"
      style="
              -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
              border: 0;
              height: auto;
              line-height: 100%;
              outline: none;
              text-decoration: none;
            "
    />

    <div style="padding: 44px 0 0; width: 410px;">
      <img
        style="width: 315px;"
        src="https://s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/html-bag.s3.getbud.co/images/assigned-check-mark.png"
        alt="duas pessoas conversando sobre uma tarefa"
      />
      <h1
        style="
              font-weight: 700;
              font-size: 21px;
              font-weight: 700;
              color: #364059;
              padding-top: 21px;
              margin-bottom: 0;
            "
      >
        Olá, {{user.first_name}}! Agora que você já usa o Bud há um tempinho, adoraríamos entender melhor como
        está sendo usar a nossa plataforma.
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div
      style="
            padding: 34px 0 0 0;
            width: 400px;
          "
    >
      <p
        style="
                font-size: 18px;
                line-height: 26px;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #525F7F;
              "
      >
        Por isso, queremos te pedir para dedicar um pouquinho do seu tempo para responder um questionário super rápido que vai nos ajudar muito! Vamos lá?
      </p>

      <div style="padding: 16px 0 0 0;">
        <a href="https://asm6am1qamy.typeform.com/to/ws7KOlJ6?utm_term=xxxxx">
        <button
          style="
                    border: 1px solid transparent;
                    border-radius: 6px;
                    background-color: #6F6EFF;
                    color: #FFFFFF;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    font-weight: 700;
                    padding: 16px 0;
                    width: 300px;
                    cursor: pointer;
                  "
        >
          Enviar Feedback
        </button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <img
    src="https://s3.sa-east-1.amazonaws.com/html-bag.s3.getbud.co/branding/bud-logotype-grayscale-sm.png"
    alt="Logotipo do Bud em tons de cinza"
    style="
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
            border: 0;
            height: auto;
            line-height: 100%;
            outline: none;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding-top: 34px;
          "
  />

</center>
</body>
</html>
